description: NEXT Biometrics Group ASA, together with its subsidiaries, provides fingerprint sensor technology in Asia, Europe, Africa, and North America. The company offers fingerprint sensors, sensor modules, and readers; and touchpads, face recognition software, and development kits. It sells its products to laptop and notebook, banking and finance, access control, and government ID sectors. The company also sells its fingerprint sensor technology hardware and software to distributors and original equipment manufacturers of electronic components. NEXT Biometrics Group ASA was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway.
